          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Military Amnesty Prevention Act</strong></p> <p>This bill permits the enlistment into the Armed Forces of aliens other than U.S. nationals and permanent resident aliens when such enlistment is vital to the U.S. national interest only if such individuals are in lawful immigration status.</p>]]></text>
        </item>
